	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64392642"><p>"Doubling the life of your EV's battery or even your smartphone's battery is no small thing,"</p><p>And it may be a bigger thing that the trivial suggestion offered here.  And also it may be valueless.  How many smartphones benefit from a doubling of cycle life, if that were possible?  And how does the charging profile interact with battery usage (which is much different for EVs and smartphones).</p><p>More interested in developments of the batteries themselves, not this.</p></div>
