		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64392704"><p>Dendrites is a problem for NiCd batteries. This study is about LiIon batteries where the problem if cracking in the medium the Li is embedded in and formation of a high resistance layer. According to the study, pulsed charging reduces both effects.</p></div>
